display_long_description:
Welcome to "Fish Tycoon," an immersive idle game experience now available on Meta Quest. Step into the vibrant underwater world where you can hatch, raise, and manage an array of exotic fish species. Begin your journey with basic tanks, slowly expanding your empire by upgrading aquariums, unlocking advanced breeding techniques, and discovering rare and legendary fish.

Balance your resources wisely to optimize growth, trade valuable species, and earn rewards to reinvest in your thriving aquatic haven. Each fish has unique traits and values, making every discovery an exciting step forward. With beautiful graphics, engaging progression mechanics, and a tranquil oceanic soundtrack, "Fish Tycoon" is perfect for casual gamers and strategy enthusiasts.

Whether you're designing a visually stunning aquarium or chasing rare fish for profit, "Fish Tycoon" offers endless possibilities. Dive into the peaceful waters and create your ultimate underwater empire. The ocean is full of opportunities—are you ready to seize them? Download now and start your tycoon adventure today!
